msgid "As I thought... the internet is not working."
msgstr "就跟我想的一样...没网了。"

msgid "Thankfully, I saved that post as a PDF."
msgstr "幸好，我把那个帖子保存为PDF了。"

msgid "\"What to do if you mess up bus ritual\""
msgstr "“搞砸了巴士仪式要怎么办”"

msgid ""
"[color=green]spikyTrap2, 1 year ago[/color]\n"
"i was about to do the bus ritual, and saw that there are no clues about what to do if the bus doesnt come or something"
msgstr ""
"[color=green]spikyTrap2, 1年前[/color]\n"
"我马上就要做巴士仪式了，但是我不知道如果巴士没来要怎么办"

msgid "someone here said that leaving a ritual half-done can be rly bad, so i'm just asking to be safe"
msgstr "有人说只做一半的仪式是很糟糕的事情，所以我就是想问问，保险点"

msgid ""
"[color=green]miko_baby, 1 year ago[/color]\n"
"I don't guarantee this will work, as I haven't personally tried the bus ritual. But! My family works at a shrine so I have some experience with banishing spirits. The steps should be:"
msgstr ""
"[color=green]miko_baby，1年前[/color]\n"
"不保真，因为我没有亲自试过巴士仪式。但是！ 我的家人在神社工作，所以我有一些驱鬼的经验。步骤如下："

msgid ""
"1) Untie the red string or thread or whatever you used from the phone.\n"
"2) Take a whole bunch of salt, any salt, and pour it in front of any exit doors of your home (indoors)."
msgstr ""
"1）解下电话上你挂的红线之类的东西。\n"
"2）取一大把盐，随便什么盐，倒在家里（室内）的每个出口前。"

msgid ""
"Make sure to pour salt on EVERY exit (windows aren't necessary though).\n"
"That's all! Hope this helps!"
msgstr ""
"每 一 个 出口都要（窗户倒是不必）。\n"
"如上！希望能帮到你！"

msgid ""
"[color=green]spikyTrap2, 1 year ago[/color]\n"
"thanks!"
msgstr ""
"[color=green]spikyTrap2，1年前[/color]\n"
"谢谢！"

msgid "[User marked this thread as solved]"
msgstr "【用户标记问题已解决】"

msgid "In other words, remove the red string from the phone and scatter salt in front of the front door, the back door and the garage door."
msgstr "换而言之，移除电话上的红线，在前面、后面和车库门口撒盐就可以。"

msgid "It sounds a little weak for a ritual but... it's better than nothing."
msgstr "对于仪式来说的话，强度有点弱...但是总比没有好。"

msgid "I'd rather not change right now..."
msgstr "我宁可现在不换的好..."

msgid "My digital alarm clock."
msgstr "我的电子闹钟。"

msgid "I'm so used to pushing snooze on this thing-"
msgstr "我已经习惯去按“懒觉”键了——"

msgid "I hope I don't do it again out of reflex and ruin the ritual."
msgstr "我希望我不会因为条件反射再这样做一次，从而毁掉仪式。"

msgid "Set it for midnight?"
msgstr "要设置到午夜吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_alarmclock.choice.Set it for midnight?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_alarmclock.choice.Set it for midnight?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "It's done."
msgstr "搞定了。"

msgid "It's set to ring at midnight."
msgstr "设定在午夜响起。"

msgid "My bed."
msgstr "我的床。"

msgid "Go to sleep?"
msgstr "要去睡觉吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_bed.choice.Go to sleep?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_bed.choice.Go to sleep?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "There's something I need to tell Hiro first."
msgstr "有些事情我得先去和希罗谈谈。"

msgid "I should take the stuff I left by the window, or I'm going to forget it here."
msgstr "我应该把我放在窗边的东西拿走，不然我会忘在这里的。"

msgid "I need to finish cleaning up the ritual first..."
msgstr "我需要先完成仪式的清扫工作..."

msgid "A book on the occult."
msgstr "一本关于神秘学的书。"

msgid "Read a passage?"
msgstr "要看一段吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_book.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_book.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "\"Salt is important when dealing with demons. For best results, a handful must be thrown at the target.\""
msgstr "“对付恶魔时，盐很重要。为了达到最好的效果，请务必抓满满一手扔在目标上。”"

msgid "A bookshelf with school related books."
msgstr "书架上摆放着与学校有关的书籍。"

msgid "Manga and other non-academic stuff gets to go in the bottom compartment."
msgstr "漫画和其他非学术性的东西放在最下面的隔层里。"

msgid "Blue... Pink... Looks like I don't have any red markers."
msgstr "蓝的...粉的...看起来我没有红色马克笔。"

msgid "Maybe in my parents' room?"
msgstr "可能在父母的房间里？"

msgid "Maybe downstairs?"
msgstr "可能在楼下？"

msgid "My computer chair."
msgstr "我的电脑椅。"

msgid "The instructions are simple enough. No need to check again."
msgstr "教程非常简单。没必要再看一次了。"

msgid "Sit at the computer?"
msgstr "要坐在电脑面前吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_computer.choice.Sit at the computer?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.misc_computer.choice.Sit at the computer?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "A gaming console."
msgstr "一台游戏主机。"

msgid "There's no time for games right now."
msgstr "现在没有打游戏的时间了。"

msgid "My computer. It's always on."
msgstr "我的电脑。一直开着。"

msgid "My desk."
msgstr "我的桌子。"

msgid "The mugs pile up here. The drawers contain school papers."
msgstr "这里堆着杯子。抽屉里放着学校的试卷。"

msgid "Leftover orange juice."
msgstr "喝剩的橘子汁。"

msgid "It's too warm to drink now."
msgstr "现在喝太热了。"

msgid "Some blank paper."
msgstr "一些白纸。"

msgid "I doodle sometimes."
msgstr "我有时候会涂鸦。"

msgid "A plant."
msgstr "一株植物。"

msgid "The best plant in this house."
msgstr "这是我们屋子里最好的植物了。"

msgid "Some cute posters."
msgstr "一些可爱的海报。"

msgid "A fancy glass table."
msgstr "一张漂亮的玻璃桌。"

msgid "An overflowing trash can."
msgstr "一个溢满的垃圾桶。"

msgid "Since you're the one who filled it up, there's no point in emptying it."
msgstr "既然你是把它装满的人，那你就没必要把它清空。"

msgid "My trash can."
msgstr "我的垃圾桶。"

msgid "A TV."
msgstr "一台电视。"

msgid "This TV is solely used to dock the game console."
msgstr "这台电视只是用来连接游戏机的。"

msgid "It's too dark to see right now."
msgstr "现在太暗了，看不清。"

msgid "A window."
msgstr "一扇窗户。"

msgid "A cozy gaming space by the window."
msgstr "窗户旁的舒适游戏空间。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Various bows and hair decorations."
msgstr "各种蝴蝶结和发饰。"

msgid "There's some red ribbon here."
msgstr "这里有一些红丝线。"

msgid "Take ${item:ch1.ribbon}?"
msgstr "要取走${item:ch1.ribbon}吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bows.choice.Take ${item:ch1.ribbon}?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bows.choice.Take ${item:ch1.ribbon}?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bundle_1.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Some clothes I got as a gift. It's not time to open them yet."
msgstr "我收到了一些衣服作为礼物。但现在还不是打开它们的时候。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bundle_1.dlg.narrator"
msgid "Some clothes."
msgstr "一些衣服。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bundle_2.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Some clothes I got as a gift. It's not time to open them yet."
msgstr "我收到了一些衣服作为礼物。但现在还不是打开它们的时候。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bundle_2.dlg.narrator"
msgid "Some clothes."
msgstr "一些衣服。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bundle_3.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Some clothes I got as a gift. It's not time to open them yet."
msgstr "我收到了一些衣服作为礼物。但现在还不是打开它们的时候。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Home_2F_Bedroom_A.pnc_wardrobe_bundle_3.dlg.narrator"
msgid "Some clothes."
msgstr "一些衣服。"

msgid "A calendar. It's still stuck in March, 6 months ago."
msgstr "日历。还停留在6个月前的3月份。"

msgid "Is there even a point in turning the pages?"
msgstr "还有翻下去的必要吗？"

msgid "The year is more or less over anyways."
msgstr "不管怎么说，今年差不多快结束了。"

msgid "Lacie's diary."
msgstr "莱西的日记。"

msgid "I don't feel like going through it right now."
msgstr "我现在没心情去看它。"

msgid "I should take all of this with me."
msgstr "我应该把这个带在身边。"

msgid "My notebook, to organize my thoughts..."
msgstr "我的笔记本，用来整理思绪..."

msgid "...the rune for the ritual..."
msgstr "...为仪式准备的符文石..."

msgid "...salt, for self defense..."
msgstr "...还有盐，自我防卫用的..."

msgid "...and finally, this thing."
msgstr "...最后还有，这个玩意。"

msgid "If the information I got is accurate, then this is my ticket back home."
msgstr "如果我的消息没错的话，这就是我回家的车票。"

msgid "(You placed the letter and to-do list into the notebook.)"
msgstr "（你把信封和待办清单放进了笔记本。）"

msgid "A happy little green plant."
msgstr "一株快乐的绿色小植物。"

msgid "It doesn't need a lot of watering, thankfully..."
msgstr "幸好它不需要经常浇水..."

msgid "Your TamaGhost™."
msgstr "你的拓麻鬼仔™。"

msgid "I already fed it today."
msgstr "我今天已经喂过它了。"

msgid "(You fed your TamaGhost™)."
msgstr "（你投喂了你的拓麻鬼仔™）。"

msgid "An umbrella."
msgstr "一把雨伞。"

msgid "It's nice outside."
msgstr "外面天气还不错。"

msgid "But not nice enough to want to go back out."
msgstr "但还没好到想再出去的地步。"
